        <mxCell id="49" value="Flow Summary&#xa;1) ModuleTrait.add_step() gives linear nodes&#xa;2) from_linear_steps builds ModuleDagDefinition&#xa;3) ModuleDagCompiler.compile validates graph and builds Dag&#xa;4) ModuleNodeDagAdapter bridges node trait to DagNodeTrait&#xa;5) DagScheduler executes nodes with NodeExecutionContext/TaskPayload&#xa;6) Node I/O contract remains Request/Response/TaskOutputEvent/TaskParserEvent" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fillColor=#D5E8D4;strokeColor=#82B366;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="40">
